{"tid":2127543,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唔明點解依家啲女咁唔知醜","createTime":"2020-07-27T11:23:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-27T13:43:13.000Z","uid":26006,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"e0746cfe576ac837561c0993c0393ff1365a7056","tid":2127543,"uid":26006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T11:23:43.000Z","msg":"話說我哥呢排識咗條新女<br />\n成日帶上嚟過夜 <br />\n一住就住住幾日<br />\n日日係房數唔知做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成家人未食完飯都好意思自己入房先<br />\n見到人又唔打招呼<br />\n去完個廁所就成日都有垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上次仲放對con喺刷牙個水杯度 我老母差啲入咗口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要聽到過佢地扑嘢好幾次<br />\n好撚困擾<br />\n我自己本身有情緒病同社交焦慮<br />\n好怕有陌生人喺屋企 又好難訓到<br />\n佢地就成撚日凌晨出房整嘢食沖涼<br />\n我就好撚躁 要食安眠藥先訓到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n已經屌過佢唔只一次 點先可以趕條柒頭走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b51941661f738011e6094c9fa3d1e85f5c941e8a","tid":2127543,"uid":26006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T11:25:05.000Z","msg":"佢仲要放啲bra底褲喺度洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b45bee7c363f273623c9d4acd6a7ac8fff7c5649","tid":2127543,"uid":343268,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T11:25:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1314d492c3c63055e086ecdf231c620cbd123d31","tid":2127543,"uid":298385,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T11:26:01.000Z","msg":"我自己本身有情緒病同社交焦慮<br />\n<br />\n首先，明示暗示比條女知你有呢個病<br />\n然後，再搵日係廳到睇人肉叉燒包呢類型既戲"},{"pid":"90958d255061423ca0a51d7c268940fcfd0bb4b9","tid":2127543,"uid":26006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1314d492c3c63055e086ecdf231c620cbd123d31","tid":2127543,"uid":298385,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T11:26:01.000Z","msg":"我自己本身有情緒病同社交焦慮<br />\n<br />\n首先，明示暗示比條女知你有呢個病<br />\n然後，再搵日係廳